            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "It's quite subjective - for me, bold text works well and makes headings stand out more clearly than just using a different color, since it explicitly marks them as \"more important\", and I'm fine with less colorful output.\n\nYou're free to adjust this to your own preference with the `:highlight` command, but I don't see any objective reason to make this change the default for everyone.",
